到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d12f5b4632cf283194f6f8ad302716dbfb85267d","tid":1541194,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3ca9b67c796152a614772132fe7762a33b2280f","tid":1541194,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"叫完落去跑步"},{"pid":"b35814352e9f90298ac538176cfca052db6a80e0","tid":1541194,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4f58bff188967e2d1d92f7817d715efc5749ddd","tid":1541194,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4faaed6748474e675827c2298c43debd29d18599","tid":1541194,"uid":240231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8151f196dfcc77e43ceed739b6757851af48ca28","tid":1541194,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"Go go go go"},{"pid":"4031a82883f22d101dc16513c0515f3a9d648ac6","tid":1541194,"uid":124685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"仲有3分鐘"},{"pid":"c83d3df357776a00cc3d3a83e07eac1d6581a702","tid":1541194,"uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"一日未達成五大訴求，一日都唔會停"},{"pid":"daf8611f07a0e54251426ed7b530742e74481229","tid":1541194,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"120ceeacc8681f8e97ec0935e35c7f9b1212a6a5","tid":1541194,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"2分鐘"},{"pid":"8258576fea883ad5aba1c401d9cf518910a78b75","tid":154